<h2>Verifying Correctness</h2>
<h6 class="subheader"></h6>
</div>
<hr class="dotted" />
<div id="articleFullText" class="col1 floatLeft firstCol">
<span class="byline">
By Leah Hoffmann
<br/>
Communications of the ACM,
March 2024,
Vol. 67 No. 3, Pages 108-ff<br/>
10.1145/3639575<br/>
<a href="#comments">Comments</a>
</span>
